---
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import SideMenu from "../../components/SideMenu.astro";
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import MainColumn from "../../layouts/MainColumn.astro";
---

<Layout title="Introduction | Zerolines.js" active="Introduction">
  <Header />
  <div class="max-w-screen-lg mx-auto lg:flex lg:space-x-12 py-12">
    <SideMenu active="Introduction" />
    <MainColumn title="Introduction">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <p>
            You don't need to prepare simple JS scripts any more for common
            components such as Modal, Tab, Dropdown Menu, etc.
          </p>
          <p class="">
            Zerolines.js is a headless UI components for not writing any lines
            of JavaScript Code. You only need attaching roll and behavior in
            your HTML element with <code>data-zl</code>, then the element works
            as is.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900">However...</h4>
          <p class="">
            this library is still beta version and a work-in-progress. Bugs,
            missing features, and breaking changes are expected!
          </p>
          <p class="">
            Any Feedback is highly appreciated. Do feel free to create an issue
            or feature requests on Github Repo.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900">If you like it...</h4>
          <p></p>
          <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-start">
            <a
              href="https://github.com/shoyu777/zerolinesjs"
              target="_blank"
              class="transition hover:-translate-y-1 flex justify-center items-center w-48 py-2 bg-gray-900 rounded text-white space-x-2"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke="currentColor"
                class="w-5 h-5"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  d="M11.48 3.499a.562.562 0 011.04 0l2.125 5.111a.563.563 0 00.475.345l5.518.442c.499.04.701.663.321.988l-4.204 3.602a.563.563 0 00-.182.557l1.285 5.385a.562.562 0 01-.84.61l-4.725-2.885a.563.563 0 00-.586 0L6.982 20.54a.562.562 0 01-.84-.61l1.285-5.386a.562.562 0 00-.182-.557l-4.204-3.602a.563.563 0 01.321-.988l5.518-.442a.563.563 0 00.475-.345L11.48 3.5z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Star the Repo</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </MainColumn>
  </div>
</Layout>
